---
source: cli/tests/help.rs
expression: "help(&[\"subvolume\", \"snapshot\"])"
---
Create a snapshot of a subvolume

Usage: snapshot [OPTIONS] <SOURCE> <DEST>

Arguments:
  <SOURCE>
          Path to the source subvolume

  <DEST>
          Destination: either an existing directory (snapshot will be named
          after the source) or a full path for the new snapshot

Options:
  -r, --readonly
          Make the snapshot read-only

  -i <QGROUPID>
          Add the newly created snapshot to a qgroup (can be given multiple
          times)

  -h, --help
          Print help
